dct_title_s: Eel River Chart 5 [cartographic material] : Worthington to Clay-Putnam Co. line Ind. : chart 1 to chart 9 inclusive
dct_description_sm: Surveyed and mapped under the direction of The United States Engineer Office, Louisville, Ky. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Depths shown by soundings. "War Department"--Upper left corner of each sheet. "This survey was made by use of aerial photography, plane table stadia, chained transit traverse control and second order vertical control. Aerial photography was begun August 21st and completed October 12, 1930." Includes index map on charts 2, 5 and 9.
